{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Recognise the enrolled user and reject everyone else, in a few lines."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"1-Add-the-SDK","text":"1. Add the SDK","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Add the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Swift package"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"code":"https:\/\/github.com\/YEOMessaging\/YEOFR-SPM","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") to your project, pinned to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"exact version "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.5.6"}]},{"text":", then ","type":"text"},{"code":"import YEOFR","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The binary is "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"arm64","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"device-only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — it does not run on the simulator."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"2-Pilot-unlock-for-non-YEO-bundle-IDs","text":"2. Pilot unlock for non-YEO bundle IDs","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR is gated to YEO-owned apps by default; a non-YEO bundle id aborts on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"construction. Evaluation customers get a "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"temporary unlock code","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"bypasses the gate during a fixed pilot window — email"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"christo@yeomessaging.com","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to request one. Pass it to the initializer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(step 3). If your app’s bundle id is "},{"code":"com.youreyeonly.*","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the gate passes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"natively."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"3-Drive-everything-with-FaceTrustService","text":"3. Drive everything with `FaceTrustService`","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService"},{"type":"text","text":" is the turnkey entry point. It owns the engine, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"camera, the fused-trust pipeline (face recognition + liveness CNN +"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TrueDepth), the identity gate, and tracker persistence, and exposes two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"streams: one for live trust verdicts and one for guided enrolment."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import YEOFR","","let service = FaceTrustService(pilotUnlockCode: \"YOUR-PILOT-CODE\")","","\/\/ Attach the preview to an AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer:","\/\/   previewLayer.session = service.previewSession","","try await service.start()    \/\/ warm-up, restore enrolment, arm gate, start camera"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"4-Enrol-a-face","text":"4. Enrol a face","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"enroll(name:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" runs a short guided capture, persists the gallery, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"re-arms the identity gate. Iterate the returned stream to coach the user:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["for await step in service.enroll(name: \"Alice\") {","    switch step.phase {","    case .capturing: show(step.prompt, progress: step.poseProgress)","    case .completed: dismiss()","    case .failed:    show(step.prompt)","    @unknown default: break","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A single front pose is enough to separate the enrolled user from other"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"people. Pass "},{"code":"poses: PoseTarget.lightingAwareGallerySequence","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"capture off-axis poses + a lighting pass, which improves recall as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user turns their head."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"5-Run-live-recognition","text":"5. Run live recognition","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["for await update in service.updates() {","    switch update.status {","    case .trusted:    badge(\"TRUSTED — \\(update.matchedName ?? \"\")\", .green)","    case .notTrusted: badge(\"NOT TRUSTED\", .red)","    case .badFraming: badge(\"ADJUST FRAMING\", .orange)","    case .noFace:     badge(\"NO FACE\", .gray)","    @unknown default: break","    }","    \/\/ update.livenessGenuine \/ update.depthIsThreeD are the contributing signals.","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"update.status == .trusted","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" already fuses face recognition, liveness, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TrueDepth, with framing applied — you never pick a similarity threshold,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you never touch the identity gate (forgetting it would collapse trust"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to liveness + depth, so any live face would pass). The enrolled gallery is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"saved across launches automatically; "},{"code":"service.enrolledName","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" reflects who is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enrolled."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"See-also","text":"See also","level":2},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A complete, runnable SwiftUI app lives in the package’s "},{"code":"Examples\/FRPilot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — full API."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustUpdate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — the stream payloads."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Getting-started","generated":true,"title":"Getting started","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"role":"article","title":"QuickStart"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/QuickStart","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"article","references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FaceTrustService","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","title":"FaceTrustService","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FaceTrustService","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Turnkey entry point for on-device face recognition with fused liveness","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and TrueDepth anti-spoofing.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/updates()":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/updates()","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/updates()","title":"updates()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"updates","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AsyncStream","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"FaceTrustUpdate","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FaceTrustUpdateV"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Per-frame trust verdicts for the recognition UI. Call once and iterate;"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the stream finishes on ","type":"text"},{"code":"stop()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Newest-wins (the underlying camera","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"stream drops stale frames), so a slow consumer can’t back up memory.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/EnrollmentProgress":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/enrollmentprogress","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Progress for an in-flight enrolment capture. Yielded by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)"},{"type":"text","text":" and the stream finishes once the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"gallery is banked (or the capture can’t start)."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EnrollmentProgress"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"EnrollmentProgress"}],"title":"EnrollmentProgress"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"abstract":[{"text":"On-device face recognition with fused liveness and TrueDepth anti-spoofing.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","role":"collection","title":"YEOFR","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/enroll(name:poses:)":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/enroll(name:poses:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Enrol "},{"code":"name","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" from the live camera and return a stream of capture","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"progress. The existing frame loop drives the gallery walk; on completion","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the service persists the gallery, refreshes ","type":"text"},{"code":"enrolledName","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", resets the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"trust pipeline against the fresh gallery, and re-arms the identity gate —","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the consumer does none of that."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"enroll"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"name"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"poses"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PoseTarget","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR10PoseTargetO"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AsyncStream","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"EnrollmentProgress","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR18EnrollmentProgressV"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"title":"enroll(name:poses:)"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustUpdate":{"abstract":[{"text":"One per-frame trust readout, with the framing gate already applied — so the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumer renders a state, not a fusion of raw signals. Yielded by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/updates()","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustUpdate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustUpdate","role":"symbol","title":"FaceTrustUpdate","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustupdate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustUpdate"}],"kind":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"value":"occ","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace"},{"value":null,"path":"\/topicSections","op":"add"},{"value":[{"title":"Getting started","identifiers":[],"anchor":"Getting-started","generated":true}],"path":"\/seeAlsoSections","op":"replace"}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}